    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think the same functionality should also be available on the client, the client should be able to inspect the servers peerCertificate data. \r\n\r\nRelated, it would be great if some events could be exposed on the nodejs client (see #8117), including an event that enables peerCertificate validation.\r\n\r\nShould this be created as a separate PR? "
